# SLI – Smart Logistics Information
**Dräxlmaier Jemmel – Internal Feeding Performance Dashboard**

Phase 1: INR Feeding (4 lines)  
Future: COC, MM, Basis, R/S, etc.

### Features
- 5-level role-based access control
- Clean English interface (German translation ready)
- Responsive Bootstrap 5 design
- Ready for internal server or GitHub + free PHP hosting

### Roles & Access
| Role             | Matricule Prefix | Access Level                              |
|------------------|------------------|-------------------------------------------|
| Directeur        | D1600xxxx        | Full system access                        |
| Sous-Directeur   | sd1600xxxx       | Department only (e.g. MH)                 |
| Supervisor MH    | s1600xxxx        | All MH data + user management             |
| Team Leader      | tl1600xxxx       | Assigned lines only                       |
| Opérateur        | O1600xxxx        | Own line only                             |

Demo password for all accounts: **demo123**
